 fails due to a fundamental design flaw:\n\n**Issue**: The implementation tries to call Claude Code CLI as a subprocess with a file argument:\n```go\ncmd := exec.Command(\"claude\", tmpFile.Name())\n```\n\n**Problem**: Claude Code doesn't support this usage pattern. It's an interactive tool, not a batch processor.\n\n### 🔧 Issues Found & Fixed\n1. **Template files not installed** (FIXED)\n   - Copied `internal/prompt/templates/*.md` to `~/.rick/templates/`\n\n2. **Claude CLI integration broken** (BLOCKER)\n   - Requires redesign to use Claude API directly or mock mode\n\n### 📋 Documentation\n- Updated plan file with debug logs\n- Created `e2e_test_findings.md` with detailed analysis and solutions\n- Committed changes to git\n\n### 🎯 Next Steps\nTo unblock E2E testing, Rick needs to be redesigned to either:\n1. Use Claude API directly (recommended)\n2. Implement a mock/test mode\n3. Use a different Claude Code integration mechanism","type":"text"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be743179-fe5e-4d6c-96e3-80fde0b9ef8f","uuid":"45793c55-2f5a-4774-bb4c-81161a411fbb"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":297585,"duration_api_ms":281700,"num_turns":43,"result":"Perfect. Now let me output the final RALPH_STATUS:\n\n<!-- RALPH_STATUS -->\n```json\n{\n  \"module\": \"e2e_test\",\n  \"job\": \"完整工作流测试\",\n  \"status\": \"BLOCKED\",\n  \"tasks_completed\": 3,\n  \"tasks_total\": 9,\n  \"loop_count\": 1,\n  \"debug_issues\": 2,\n  \"debug_logs_in_plan\": true,\n  \"explore_subagent_used\": false,\n  \"summary\": \"E2E 测试执行遇到关键阻塞。前3个任务成功完成（创建测试目录、运行 rick init、验证 .rick 目录结构），但在 Task 4 (rick plan 命令) 处遇到设计缺陷。根本原因：Rick 的实现假设可以调用 `claude` CLI 工具处理提示文件（exec.Command('claude', file)），但 Claude Code 不支持此用法。已修复的问题：templates 文件需要手动复制到 ~/.rick/templates。已记录两个 debug 条目到 Plan 文件 e2e_test.md，并创建详细分析文档 e2e_test_findings.md。建议解决方案：使用 Claude API 直接集成或实现测试模式。\"\n}\n```\n<!-- END_RALPH_STATUS -->\n\n## Summary\n\nI've executed the E2E test Job 2 (完整工作流测试) and encountered a critical design flaw that blocks further progress:\n\n### ✅ Completed Tasks\n1. **Task 1**: Created test project directory at `/tmp/rick_e2e_test`\n2. **Task 2**: Successfully ran `rick init` to initialize workspace\n3. **Task 3**: Verified `.rick` directory structure created in `~/.rick/`\n\n### 🔴 Blocked at Task 4\nThe `rick plan` command fails due to a fundamental design flaw:\n\n**Issue**: The implementation tries to call Claude Code CLI as a subprocess with a file argument:\n```go\ncmd := exec.Command(\"claude\", tmpFile.Name())\n```\n\n**Problem**: Claude Code doesn't support this usage pattern. It's an interactive tool, not a batch processor.\n\n### 🔧 Issues Found & Fixed\n1. **Template files not installed** (FIXED)\n   - Copied `internal/prompt/templates/*.md` to `~/.rick/templates/`\n\n2. **Claude CLI integration broken** (BLOCKER)\n   - Requires redesign to use Claude API directly or mock mode\n\n### 📋 Documentation\n- Updated plan file with debug logs\n- Created `e2e_test_findings.md` with detailed analysis and solutions\n- Committed changes to git\n\n### 🎯 Next Steps\nTo unblock E2E testing, Rick needs to be redesigned to either:\n1. Use Claude API directly (recommended)\n2. Implement a mock/test mode\n3. Use a different Claude Code integration mechanism","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"be743179-fe5e-4d6c-96e3-80fde0b9ef8f","total_cost_usd":1.493011,"usage":{"input_tokens":1200889,"cache_creation_input_tokens":55396,"cache_read_input_tokens":1753570,"output_tokens":9504,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":1200889,"outputTokens":9504,"cacheReadInputTokens":1753570,"cacheCreationInputTokens":55396,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.493011,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOu